#

Savory Cheddar Waffles

25 min
$8.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairyglutenegg

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

breakfast

Tags:

brunchsnackeasysavory

Description

Deliciously cheesy waffles perfect for brunch or a snack, packed with flavor and easy to make!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • baking powder: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • milk: 1 1/2 cups
  • egg: 1 large
  • sharp cheddar cheese, shredded: 1 cup
  • unsalted butter, melted: 1/4 cup
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1/2 teaspoon
